<section class="about">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>Ariel Shamir is a professor of Computer Science specializing in computer graphics, geometry processing, image and video processing, and visualization.</p>
  <p>His research spans topics including shape analysis, content-aware image resizing (seam carving), 3D modeling and fabrication, animation, and information visualization.</p>
